videos.headline: Diana Taurasi drains early 3 for the Mercury
videos.description: Diana Taurasi scores the first points of the game for the Mercury with a fadeaway 3.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Diana Taurasi drains early 3 for the Mercury) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rhyne Howard erases shot at the rim
videos.description: Rhyne Howard swats a shot out of bounds to deny the Mercury from scoring.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Rhyne Howard erases shot at the rim) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Diana Taurasi absorbs contact for and-1 bucket
videos.description: Diana Taurasi scores at the rim for the Mercury despite being fouled.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Diana Taurasi absorbs contact for and-1 bucket) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Diana Taurasi makes history as first 10,000-point scorer in WNBA history
videos.description: Mercury star Diana Taurasi drills a 3 from way downtown to become the first player in WNBA history to reach 10,000 career points.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Diana Taurasi makes history as first 10,000-point scorer in WNBA history) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taurasi keeps scoring with smooth step-back jumper
videos.description: Diana Taurasi knocks down a contested jump shot for the Mercury.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Taurasi keeps scoring with smooth step-back jumper) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taurasi reaches 10,000-point milestone during 42-point outburst
videos.description: Diana Taurasi has a night to remember, dropping 42 points and becoming the first WNBA player to score 10,000 career points.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (Taurasi reaches 10,000-point milestone during 42-point outburst) 2023/08/04 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Diana Taurasi up to 42 points after wild 3 while falling out of bounds
videos.description: Diana Taurasi becomes the oldest player in WNBA history to reach 40 points with this off-balance 3-pointer for the Mercury.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Diana Taurasi up to 42 points after wild 3 while falling out of bounds) 2023/08/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Diana Taurasi thankful for support on historic night
videos.description: Diana Taurasi addresses the Phoenix crowd after becoming the first WNBA player to reach 10,000 points.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Diana Taurasi thankful for support on historic night) 2023/8/3 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mercury honor Taurasi with 'one-of-a-kind' gifts
videos.description: The Phoenix Mercury gift Diana Taurasi with a trio of special items to honor her for reaching the 10,000-point mark.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Mercury honor Taurasi with 'one-of-a-kind' gifts) 2023/8/3 ESHEET
